title: Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jaha
content:
(Chorus)
Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jahan,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila – 2
Jaise Tune Kiya Hai Kshama,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila – 2
Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jahan,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila

Verse 1
Paapo Ka Tha Karz Mujhpe Jo Bhari,
Dukho Me Zindagi Guzari Thi Saari

Mere Gunaho Se Mujhko Bachane,
Tune Khuda Apni Zindagi Thi Wari – 2

Tune Kar Di Hai Kimat Ada,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila

Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jahan,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila

Verse 2
Duniya Ke Aage Duhaai Bahut Di,
Aansu Ke Bin Na Mila Mujhko Kuchh Bhi

Tujhko Mila Jab Mai Tab Tujhko Jana,
Tab Tere Aage Jo Maine Dua Ki – 2

Tune Sun Li Hai Meri Dua,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila

Maine Dhundha Ye Sara Jahan,
Tere Jaisa Na Koi Mila

title: Hazaaron Zubane Lyrics Ft. Amit Kamble, Prakruthi Angelina & Hemant Sharma
content:
Saari shristi par
Tera adhikaar
Tu rajadhiraaj hai prabhu

Tujhse hai zameen
Tujhi see aasmaan
Jag ka tu maalik prabhu

Pre-chorus 1:
Karte hai sajda,
Ibaadat ho teri sadaa

Chorus:
Hazaaron zubaane gayein
Tera hi naam dohraayein
Yeshu tu pravitra hai

Verse 2:
Unch neech ka
Na koi wajood
Tere rajya mein
Tere rajya mein

Har kisi ka hai
Swaagat yahan
Tere rajya mein
Tere rajya mein

Pre-chorus 2:
Teri rehmat mein hi
Tu leta hai sabko kareeb

Chorus:
Hazaaron zubaane gayein
Tera hi naam dohraayein
Yeshu tu pravitra hai

Bridge:
Shahon ka shah hai tu khuda
Tera na koi muqaabla
Tera hi takht rahe sabse uncha

title: Praise lyrics feat. Brandon Lake, Chris Brown & Chandler Moore, Elevation Worship
creator: Elevation Worship
content:
Let everything that has breath
Praise the Lord
Praise the Lord

I’ll praise in the valley
Praise on the mountain
I’ll praise when I’m sure
Praise when I’m doubting

I’ll praise when outnumbered
Praise when surrounded
Cause praise is the waters
My enemies drown in

As long as I’m breathing
I’ve got a reason to

Praise the Lord
Oh my soul
Praise the Lord
Oh my soul

I’ll praise when I feel it
I’ll praise when I don’t
I’ll praise cause I know
You’re still in control

My praise is a weapon
It’s more than a sound
My praise is the shout
That brings Jericho down

Praise the Lord
Oh my soul
Praise the Lord
Oh my soul
I won’t be quiet
My God is alive
How could I keep it inside
Praise the Lord oh my soul

I’ll praise cause You’re sovereign
Praise cause You reign
Praise cause You rose and defeated the grave

I’ll praise cause You’re faithful
Praise cause You’re true
Praise cause there’s nobody greater than You
